        "vlmDescription": "A light-blue rounded rectangular pill shape, thicker-walled than a simple trim, filling the viewport. Identity verified by pixel-diff baseline, not VLM \u2014 visually similar to Brep-Trim.",
        "whatItDoes": "Trims a source field to a closed Brep and adds a sealed shell along the boundary. union(max(F, brep_SDF), shellBand). shellInner > 0 extends INTO the body, shellOuter > 0 extends OUTWARD.",
        "whatYouShouldSee": "A light-blue rounded pill \u2014 trimmed field plus a sealed shell band. Distinguish from Brep-Trim by the added shell thickness."
    },
    "actions": [
        {
            "type": "WaitForGrasshopperSolution",
            "timeoutMs": 5000
        },
        {
            "type": "GrasshopperSetToggle",
